INFO:

Our story takes place in a world called ôIvalice,ö in an age when 
magic was commonplace and airships plied the skies û the Archadian 
Empire, seeking to strengthen its base of power, had been invading 
and subjugating its neighboring lands one by oneùa fate which befell 
the small Kingdom of Dalmasca. Archadia's invasion and the subsequent 
death of the Dalmascan king prompted the Princess Ashe, the sole 
surviving heir to the Dalmascan throne, to take up arms against the 
invaders. In her struggle to oust the occupying Archadian forces and 
restore freedom to her people, Ashe must watch as many of her allies 
pay the blood price for that freedom. Though tempted to abandon all 
hope in the face of the Empire's might, her determination keeps her 
from succumbing before what would seem to be inevitable defeat. Then 
she meets Vaan, an urchin from the Dalmascan capital of Rabanastre. 
Vaan dreams of one day becoming a sky pirate, escaping the Empire on 
his airship. Vaan, Ashe, Vaan's friend Penelo, the sky pirate Balthier, 
his partner Fran and many more are on an adventure through Ivalice that 
traces the mysteries behind the Archadian Empire's invasion.

